title: ACSI - Christian Education
description:
4 books needed for Association of Christian School International (ACSI) certification:

Foundations of Christian School Education (2003) by James Braley, Jack Layman, and Ray White

Love God with All Your Mind (1997) by J.P. Moreland, with as Dallas Willard general editor

Reclaiming the Future of Christian Education (1998) by Albert E. Greene

Truth and Transformation a Manifesto for Ailing Nations (2009) by Vishal Magalwadi
